## Test File Organization

### Colocated Unit Tests (Preferred)

```
src/
├── lib/
│   ├── permissions.ts
│   ├── permissions.test.ts    <- right next to the source
│   ├── pagination.ts
│   └── pagination.test.ts
├── components/
│   ├── ItemCard.tsx
│   └── ItemCard.test.tsx
```

### Separate Integration & E2E Tests

```
tests/
├── integration/
│   ├── auth.test.ts           # Test auth API endpoints
│   ├── resources.test.ts      # Test resource CRUD endpoints
│   └── workflows.test.ts      # Test workflow features
├── e2e/
│   ├── auth.spec.ts           # Full authentication flow through UI (if your project has auth)
│   ├── setup.spec.ts          # Full setup flow
│   └── main-feature.spec.ts   # Primary feature data loading
└── fixtures/                  # Shared test data
    ├── users.ts
    └── records.ts
```

